-- Use the `ref` function to select from other models

select *
from DATA_SCIENCE.UAY3YB_RAW.my_first_dbt_model
where id = 1

SELECT
    13                                   AS week_number,
    COUNT(DISTINCT symbol)               AS total_unique_stocks,
    AVG(price)                           AS average_weekly_price,
    MAX(price_change)                    AS max_price_change,
    MAX(price_percent_change)            AS max_price_change_percent
FROM DATA_SCIENCE.UAY3YB_RAW.raw_wsj

SELECT
    symbol,
    COUNT(*) AS appearance_count
FROM DATA_SCIENCE.UAY3YB_RAW.raw_wsj
GROUP BY symbol
HAVING COUNT(*) > 1
ORDER BY appearance_count DESC

SELECT
    13                                   AS week_number,   -- spring‑break week
    AVG(price)                           AS avg_price,
    AVG(price_change)                    AS avg_price_change,
    AVG(price_percent_change)            AS avg_price_change_percent
FROM DATA_SCIENCE.UAY3YB_RAW.raw_wsj
